00:17:05.524 --> 00:17:06.442
Sang-woo.

00:17:11.780 --> 00:17:13.323
C'est joli.

00:17:14.366 --> 00:17:15.409
Monsieur.

00:17:18.537 --> 00:17:21.290
Vous avez 30 minutes.

00:17:21.373 --> 00:17:23.208
